<item>
            <title>[LU-13145] LNet Health: increase transaction timeout</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13145</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On larger clusters it appears like the current transaction timeout default of 10 seconds is too short and it causes RDMA timeouts.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The proposal is to increase the timeout to 150s. With a retry count of 3 that would bring the LND timeout to 50s, which was the initial value before health.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="57816">LU-13145</key>
            <summary>LNet Health: increase transaction timeout</summary>
